Anyone that has caught the modification or tuning bug can understand the meaning behind their brand name: even if it's "done", it's never really done. cleanDesc: PSDesigns M3 GTS Style Arm Rest Delete Panel
short-description: Designed to replace the factory Arm Rest, the PSDesigns GTS Arm Rest Delete Panel (A.R.D.) offers a cost effective aesthetically pleasing alternative to the OEM offering. As used in PSDesigns' BMW E92 M3 GTS style builds, this piece finishes interiors off nicely and provides the same look as the factory GTS. Trimmed in genuine Alcantara fabric The factory arm rest can hinder driver control when driving on the limit. The GTS Style arm rest delete removes this potential hazard and saves weight at the same time. BMW created the M3 GTS as a purpose built, turnkey track ready car. While most look to the performance parts found on the GTS as evidence of BMW's dedication to creating a track-ready car, the host of weight reduction and safety options are just as important. The BMW M3 GTS was equipped with a multitude of safety components and weight saving alternatives that enabled track driving with reduced risk, including fixed back seats with capacity to accommodate racing harnesses, a roll bar with specific harness mounts and head padding, Arm Rest Delete and even a fire extinguisher (available in other listings). Now available to order for your GTS Style or track car build. A great addition to any GTS style interior, show car or track car build at a fraction of the OEM price of $1500! This item will fit any BMW E9X generation 3 series BMW, E90, E91, E92 and E93 models. Press fit installation and easily removed to access USB, AUX and 12v Socket. PSDesigns is an enthusiast based company that specializes in niche performance upgrades. From intake conversions to handling upgrades, they have innovated and tested in real world environments to bring you high performance components.
